tmpl::simple -title "Invitation-Only Network of Trusted Friends" {

    blockquote {
	b {
	    t "Our apologies!.."
	}

	p

	t "phigita.net is unique, because it's an organically growing network of trusted friends. That way we won't grow too large, too quickly and everyone will have at least one person to vouch for them."

	p

	t "If you know someone who is a trusted member of phigita.net, that person can invite you to join as well. If you don't know a phigita.net trusted member, wait a bit and most likely you soon will."

	p

	t "We look forward to having you as part of the phigita.net community."

    }

}
